      HAAAAAAHAHAHAAHAHAHAHAhahahahaha.<br /><br />*breathe*AAAAAAAAHAHAHAAHHAHAAHHAAHHAhahahahahaha.<br /><br />Oh man.<br /><br />&quot;Unnecessary&quot; as in &quot;inconvenient to us.&quot;  Nothing even close to anything close to reforms would have happened without the Snowden revelations.  If anything we've heard about - and the issue has gotten - not even 10% of what it should have.<br /><br />&quot;Unnecessary&quot;?  What a crock.  It's not even close to what we really need to happen to get this travesty straightened out.<br /><br /><br />It's been great for motivating the NSA to take action to not let more things escape that the vast majority of Americans would disapprove of, though.
      
